  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISourceLocation, IASNode, IBlockNode, IContainerNode

    public final class ConfigConditionBlockNode
extends BlockNode
    Special block node for a block gated with a configuration condition. For example: 
     CONFIG::DEBUG 
 {
     import my.debug.classes.*;
 }
